<div class="entry">
<h2 class="title">
<a href="http://jasongooljar.com/2009/03/26/video-of-ct-working-families-party-at-aig-exec-homes/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Video of CT Working Families Party at AIG Exec homes">Video of CT Working Families Party at AIG Exec homes</a>
</h2>
<p>I think it’s great that they filmed their <a href="http://www.jasongooljar.com/?p=2787" target="_blank">bus trip from last weekend</a> and put it up on the web. </p>
<span class='embed-youtube' style='text-align:center; display: block;'><iframe class='youtube-player' type='text/html' width='640' height='390' src='http://www.youtube.com/embed/lcNo2KEdXEQ?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;fs=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;wmode=transparent' frameborder='0'></iframe></span>
